record FpML5.legal.ActualPrice {
  # Specifies the currency associated with the net price. This element is not present if the price is expressed in percentage terms (as specified through the priceExpression element).
  currency : string?

  # Specifies the net price amount. In the case of a fixed income security or a convertible bond, this price includes the accrued interests.
  amount : decimal

  # Specifies whether the price is expressed in absolute or relative terms.
  priceExpression : string

  id : string?

}

currency.Doc: Specifies the currency associated with the net price. This element is not present if the price is expressed in percentage terms (as specified through the priceExpression element).
currency.Name: currency

amount.Doc: Specifies the net price amount. In the case of a fixed income security or a convertible bond, this price includes the accrued interests.
amount.Name: amount

priceExpression.Doc: Specifies whether the price is expressed in absolute or relative terms.
priceExpression.Name: priceExpression
